                                            <h2><a href="/web/20150105193604/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-30679276">Consumers and tech - does Las Vegas know what you want?</a></h2>
                                                                <p class="article-date">5 January 2015</p>
                                        <p>In the first week of January Las Vegas also becomes home to the excessive ambitions of an industry that believes it really knows what consumers want.</p>
                                            <p>
                            <a href="/web/20150105193604/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-30679276">Read full article</a>
